# Code comments language

- Write **all** code comments in **English**: `//`, `/* */`, `<!-- -->`, JSDoc/TSDoc, `TODO` / `FIXME` notes, and similar.
- User-facing strings (i18n keys, UI copy) follow product locale rules; this rule applies only to **developer comments** in source files.

```typescript
// ❌ BAD — Italian (or other non-English) in comments
// Calcola lo scrape type in base al toggle

// ✅ GOOD
// Resolve scrape type from the automatic extraction toggle
```
